1
00:00:00,390 --> 00:00:04,914
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:04,914 --> 00:00:10,418
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,418 --> 00:00:16,846
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,846 --> 00:00:21,326
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,326 --> 00:00:25,774
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,774 --> 00:00:30,685
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,685 --> 00:00:34,734
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,734 --> 00:00:39,269
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,269 --> 00:00:43,566
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,566 --> 00:00:48,331
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,331 --> 00:00:51,822
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,822 --> 00:00:55,502
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,148 --> 00:01:00,526
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,526 --> 00:01:03,214
=Episode 26=

15
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:07,966
Didn't I give you a day off?

16
00:01:07,966 --> 00:01:12,000
Can you fly?
How did you get here so quickly?

17
00:01:12,866 --> 00:01:14,080
I fly?

18
00:01:15,266 --> 00:01:16,966
Alright. You can go now.

19
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:18,666
Okay, boss.

20
00:01:22,166 --> 00:01:23,166
Wait, Miss Jin.

21
00:01:26,633 --> 00:01:27,966
Your proposal is good.

22
00:01:28,933 --> 00:01:31,266
We really ignored the market at campus.

23
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:33,566
This market has great potential.

24
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:35,433
We could turn a healthy profit in it.

25
00:01:35,433 --> 00:01:38,100
We lack such resources

26
00:01:38,333 --> 00:01:41,866
and enough funds to develop new markets.

27
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,333
So, based on cost-effectiveness
and input-output ratio,

28
00:01:44,333 --> 00:01:46,600
I have listed
three companies worth acquiring.

29
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:48,933
They specialize in the campus market.

30
00:01:49,033 --> 00:01:52,300
Good. We can acquire at a low price
and then enter the campus market.

31
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:56,600
As a subsidiary,
it can be integrated within a year.

32
00:01:56,766 --> 00:01:58,133
Yes.

33
00:01:58,133 --> 00:02:00,033
And I have put this plan

34
00:02:00,033 --> 00:02:02,166
into our new product development plan.

35
00:02:02,766 --> 00:02:03,966
I have read it.

36
00:02:04,133 --> 00:02:05,900
Your suggestion is very good.

37
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:09,266
Miss Jin, you can implement it.

38
00:02:10,866 --> 00:02:14,500
Within a quarter,
we could turn losses into profits.

39
00:02:15,566 --> 00:02:16,700
You are worthy of being my secretary.

40
00:02:17,033 --> 00:02:19,133
You've learned a lot from me.

41
00:02:20,033 --> 00:02:21,666
Thanks to my good teaching.

42
00:02:23,133 --> 00:02:24,400
- Thank you, boss.
- Alright.

43
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,233
- I'm back to work.
- Go ahead.

44
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,366
I don't want to go home.

45
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:53,900
Where do you want to go?

46
00:03:00,033 --> 00:03:01,133
How about going boxing?

47
00:03:02,066 --> 00:03:03,296
Boxing?

48
00:03:05,766 --> 00:03:06,966
I can also box.

49
00:03:08,433 --> 00:03:09,800
Are you sure you can beat me?

50
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,192
Yeah.

51
00:03:17,733 --> 00:03:19,166
I don't want anyone to get hurt.

52
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:22,166
How could I let her get hurt?

53
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,768
Please.

54
00:03:44,033 --> 00:03:46,566
So you were worried about me.

55
00:03:48,033 --> 00:03:50,500
(The new product
will be launched soon.)

56
00:03:50,866 --> 00:03:52,600
(Promotion Plan for New Products)
(All work is progressing smoothly.)

57
00:03:54,166 --> 00:03:56,000
(I'm really happy to work)

58
00:03:56,266 --> 00:03:57,566
(with boss every day.)

59
00:03:59,928 --> 00:04:03,771
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

60
00:04:03,771 --> 00:04:09,088
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

61
00:04:11,100 --> 00:04:12,256
It's over.

62
00:04:21,344 --> 00:04:22,466
Let's take a photo.

63
00:04:22,466 --> 00:04:23,488
Okay.

64
00:04:27,126 --> 00:04:29,824
♪If I had a little more time♪

65
00:04:29,824 --> 00:04:33,632
♪Let me stay longer♪

66
00:04:33,632 --> 00:04:35,904
♪Can I hold you tight♪

67
00:04:35,904 --> 00:04:38,080
♪And you say yes to me♪

68
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:43,552
♪We watch the scenery together♪

69
00:04:45,088 --> 00:04:46,304
(Research of Channel and Price)

70
00:04:47,533 --> 00:04:49,500
Are you questioning my design?

71
00:04:51,666 --> 00:04:53,766
I didn't make it up.

72
00:04:54,266 --> 00:04:56,466
It's based
on the latest market research data.

73
00:04:56,933 --> 00:04:58,466
Everyone can check the results.

74
00:04:59,966 --> 00:05:03,966
You know design? You tell me what to do.

75
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,533
No, I don't know design,

76
00:05:07,766 --> 00:05:11,500
but I know we should design
based on the core needs

77
00:05:11,666 --> 00:05:12,666
of customers.

78
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:21,733
Heard it? Note it down.

79
00:05:28,466 --> 00:05:29,600
Well done, Miss Jin.

80
00:05:30,066 --> 00:05:33,133
You quickly completed
the customer research report.

81
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:36,166
You've learned a lot from me.

82
00:05:36,733 --> 00:05:40,000
Thank you. Here is
the full research report.

83
00:05:40,266 --> 00:05:41,166
Please read it.

84
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:42,848
Okay.

85
00:05:48,833 --> 00:05:50,240
Good.

86
00:06:10,433 --> 00:06:11,712
Mother.

87
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:26,272
(Launch of the New Product)

88
00:06:38,633 --> 00:06:39,700
Mother, you're back.

89
00:06:41,033 --> 00:06:43,300
How about the sales of our new product?

90
00:06:46,266 --> 00:06:48,900
Both word of mouth
and sales have hit a historic high.

91
00:06:50,066 --> 00:06:52,400
With the profit from the campus market,

92
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,966
market share has reached

93
00:06:56,466 --> 00:06:58,966
an unprecedented 95 percent.

94
00:07:00,133 --> 00:07:01,300
95 percent?

95
00:07:01,466 --> 00:07:02,700
95 percent.

96
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,700
95 percent.

97
00:07:08,166 --> 00:07:09,933
We did it.

98
00:07:15,366 --> 00:07:17,533
I'm so happy, Miss Jin.

99
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,100
We did it.

100
00:07:29,333 --> 00:07:32,800
(WE Beauty Group launched a new product
in partnership with Gu Group.)

101
00:07:32,933 --> 00:07:35,100
(The word of mouth
and sales hit a historic high.)

102
00:07:35,166 --> 00:07:38,000
(The market share
reached an unprecedented 95 percent.)

103
00:07:43,266 --> 00:07:46,166
There is no failure once I make a move.

104
00:07:47,033 --> 00:07:48,900
With the market share of the Lan family,

105
00:07:49,666 --> 00:07:53,066
the profit from the technology shares
has exceeded 30 million yuan.

106
00:07:54,133 --> 00:07:58,066
This result has been achieved
relying on us working together.

107
00:08:04,670 --> 00:08:08,733
(95 percent.)

108
00:08:10,866 --> 00:08:12,633
(We did it.)

109
00:08:13,233 --> 00:08:15,400
(I'm so happy, Miss Jin.)

110
00:08:24,133 --> 00:08:27,733
Hello, Yuan. What does that mean?

111
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:29,966
You spoiled my good mood.

112
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:33,000
Good mood? Gu Qianqian.

113
00:08:33,133 --> 00:08:34,800
Have you forgotten our goal?

114
00:08:37,333 --> 00:08:40,166
I haven't. I told you.

115
00:08:40,633 --> 00:08:41,933
Nobody can have

116
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:44,000
what I can't get.

117
00:08:45,033 --> 00:08:47,200
You helped him make such a good product.

118
00:08:47,366 --> 00:08:49,266
Isn't this going against your goal?

119
00:08:50,166 --> 00:08:51,700
Gaining Lan's trust

120
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:54,333
is just the first step to getting him.

121
00:08:55,833 --> 00:08:57,933
Alright, I hope you remember.

122
00:08:58,566 --> 00:09:00,166
For our consistent goal,

123
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:02,500
I have a perfect method.

124
00:09:03,166 --> 00:09:05,766
You get him, and I destroy the group.

125
00:09:07,233 --> 00:09:08,200
Well, spit it out.

126
00:09:09,700 --> 00:09:11,136
Let's talk in person.

127
00:09:12,033 --> 00:09:12,966
Sounds mysterious.

128
00:09:13,866 --> 00:09:15,466
Alright, you come to me.

129
00:09:23,866 --> 00:09:25,566
This is not my fault.

130
00:09:26,466 --> 00:09:28,200
You forced me into this.

131
00:09:30,101 --> 00:09:31,316
(Lan Rensha)

132
00:09:31,966 --> 00:09:33,066
You can't blame me.

133
00:09:39,622 --> 00:09:44,144
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

134
00:09:47,174 --> 00:09:52,135
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

135
00:09:55,184 --> 00:10:01,008
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

136
00:10:01,008 --> 00:10:08,478
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

137
00:10:08,478 --> 00:10:11,959
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

138
00:10:11,959 --> 00:10:16,080
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

139
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,776
♪Open my secret♪

140
00:10:17,776 --> 00:10:23,824
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

141
00:10:23,824 --> 00:10:27,696
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

142
00:10:27,696 --> 00:10:32,202
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

143
00:10:32,202 --> 00:10:40,912
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
